HISTORY OF JAVA WEB SERVLET and JavaServer Pages (JSP)
•	Java is built naturally with internet functionality. In June 1997, Sun Microsystems announced the Java Servlet.
	Java Servlet is one of the fundamental foundation in developing different components of a Java Web which runs 
  in a single process by using grain threads.
•	While in 1998, Sun released the JavaServer Pages (JSP).
	JSP is used to easily code a dynamic HTML pages.
•	Both Servlets and JSPs lets the programmers build or develop a portable, easy to maintain, modular and scalable Web applications.
